the minimum of List is infinity if the List is empty,
otherwise the first item of the List if the first item of the List is less than the minimum of the tail of the List,
otherwise the minimum of the tail of the List.
the rest of List is list of each item in the List where the item is not equal to the minimum of the List.
List sorted is new list if the List is empty, otherwise list of the minimum of the List concatenated with: the rest of the List, sorted.

output is list of 4, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, and 7 sorted.